OL,3,CWould-be parents 'delay having
OL,4,Cchildren because of cost-of-living
OL,5,Ccrisis'
OL,7,FSarah Pennells, consumer finance
OL,8,Fspecialist at Royal London, said:
OL,9,F"We've been tracking how people have
OL,10,Fbeen responding to the financial
OL,11,Fchallenges of the rising cost of
OL,12,Fliving for more than two years and
OL,13,Fit's clear we're now starting to see
OL,14,Fthat people are making changes to
OL,15,Ftheir longer-term life plans.
