OL,3,CWould-be parents 'delay having
OL,4,Cchildren because of cost-of-living
OL,5,Ccrisis'
OL,7,F"When prices for food and energy were
OL,8,Fincreasing, we saw people cut back and
OL,9,Fmake changes to their spending and
OL,10,Fshopping habits, but now we're seeing
OL,11,Fthat some major life decisions are
OL,12,Fbeing delayed as people are weighing
OL,13,Fup whether or not they can afford to
OL,14,Fact on the plans they'd made."
OL,16,FLast week official figures showed UK
OL,17,Finflation fell to the lowest level in
OL,18,Fnearly three years in April as energy
OL,19,Fprices continued to cool.
