OL,5,Ccrisis'
OL,7,FConsumer Prices Index (CPI) inflation
OL,8,Fslowed to 2.3% in April, down from
OL,9,F3.2% in March, according to the Office
OL,10,Ffor National Statistics (ONS).
OL,12,FSharp rises in the cost of food,
OL,13,Fenergy and housing in recent years
OL,14,Fhave made the cost of living a central
OL,15,Fissue in the upcoming General Election.
