OL,3,CWould-be parents 'delay having
OL,4,Cchildren because of cost-of-living
OL,5,Ccrisis'
OL,7,FIt comes after similar research by the
OL,8,FResolution Foundation showed that the
OL,9,Fcrisis has changed what households do
OL,10,Fwith their money, with consumption
OL,11,Fbeing cut by more than the fall in
OL,12,Fincomes.
OL,14,FThe UK squeezed more than a decade's
OL,15,Fworth of "normal" inflation into just
OL,16,Fthree years, according to the
OL,17,FFoundation, which is focused on
OL,18,Fimproving the living standards for
OL,19,Fthose on low to middle incomes.
